Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
report_precision(25.10)                                report_precision(25.10)

Name
       report_precision

Syntax
       report_precision <integer>

       Default: 3

       Controls  the number of digits appearing after the decimal point in the
       report_timing,   report_net,   report_cell_instance_timing,   and   re-
       port_clocks reports. The maximum allowed value of integer is 8.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

